# UI Conventions

## Styling

This project uses **inline React styles** exclusively — no CSS modules, no styled-components, no Tailwind.

### CSS Variables (from `src/styles/index.css`)
```
var(--surface)         // Card backgrounds
var(--surface-hover)   // Hover states
var(--background)      // Page background
var(--text)            // Primary text (white)
var(--text-muted)      // Secondary text
var(--primary)         // Accent/action color
var(--border)          // Borders
var(--danger)          // Error/delete red
```

### Common Values
```typescript
padding: '0.75rem'      // Standard card padding
borderRadius: '8px'     // Cards
borderRadius: '6px'     // Buttons, badges
fontSize: '0.8rem'      // Body text
fontSize: '0.75rem'     // Small buttons
fontSize: '0.65rem'     // Badges, tags
```

### PC Compatibility
Native `<select>` and `<option>` elements don't inherit CSS variables on some PC browsers. Use explicit hex:
```typescript
style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', color: '#ffffff' }}
```

## Screen Patterns

### Collapsible Sections (GameSummaryScreen)
- Default to **collapsed** (`true`)
- Toggle header must have `color: 'var(--text)'` (white text)
- Container: `padding: '0.75rem'`, `background: '#1a1a2e'`

### Screenshot Sharing
Uses `html2canvas` to capture UI as images for WhatsApp sharing via `navigator.share()`.
- Build HTML in hidden divs, not from live DOM
- Split long content into multiple pages (3 players/card for Chronicle, 5 players/card for Forecast)
- Pre-game teaser = dedicated first screenshot
- Include page numbers: "1/3", "2/3", "3/3"

### Bottom Action Bars
Standardized sizing: `padding: '0.6rem'`, `fontSize: '0.8rem'`

### Navigation
Bottom tab bar: New Game | History | Statistics | Graphs (admin/member) | Settings. Hidden during live game, chip entry, game summary, training play.

## RTL Rules

- Use `direction: 'rtl'` on containers with Hebrew text
- Use `gap` instead of `marginRight` in flex containers
- For `html2canvas` rendered HTML, use `dir="rtl"` attribute

## Content Rules

- All section headers in English for UI chrome, Hebrew for content
- Only ONE "Poker Manager" signature at bottom of a screen, not after every card
- Headers: `<h2 className="card-title">` with `margin: 0`, consistent font size per screen
